html:
There is a secret
Walls are emerging
Farming machines
Are ready to go
Let’s go to Mars
In an Ursus tractor
We know impossible
Is in the reach
Oh Ursus tractor!
Your mechanics
Are the cream
Of socialist technology
Oh Ursus tractor!
When you burn gas
My heart beats faster
And I know you’re real
title: Ursus tractor
